data.description: Fantastic curb appeal and just as beautiful on the inside! Newer flooring and neutral paint colors throughout. This 3 bedroom, 1.75bath home has 2 living areas, dine-in kitchen, utility room & a huge backyard. New Roof 2023. New HVAC & Plumbing 2021. New Water Heater 2023. Living Room furniture, Bedroom Furniture, Refrigerator and Dining Table are all negotiable. Seller states that his loan is assumable @ an interest rate of 3.25%
